            <div class="">
                
                    <p>Localizado no coração do Rio de Janeiro, o Hilton Copacabana é o hotel de frente para a praia com mais quartos com vista para o mar de Copacabana. Próximo a aeroportos, ao centro da cidade e às principais atrações locais, ele fica a apenas 10 minutos do Pão de Açúcar e a curta distância a pé de várias opções de restaurantes. O hotel oferece 545 quartos, 36 salas de reunião flexíveis,  duas piscinas, um spa de bem-estar de serviço completo, restaurantes e bares, além de serviço na praia.</p>

	<script type="text/javascript">
		$(document).ready(function() {
			/**
			 * Update the site experience based on the window size.
			 */
			var updateSiteExperience = function() {
				var windowWidth = $(window).width();

				if(windowWidth < 420) {
					digitalData.page.attributes.siteExperience = "P";
				} else if(windowWidth < 768) {
					digitalData.page.attributes.siteExperience = "T";
				} else {
					digitalData.page.attributes.siteExperience = "D";
				}
			}

			updateSiteExperience();

			$(window).resize(updateSiteExperience);
			/**
			 * Format a date for use with Adobe Analytics.
			 *
			 * @param Date d Date object.
			 */
			var formatAADate = function(d) {
				var month = (d.getMonth() + 1).toString();

				if(month.length === 1) {
					month = "0" + month;
				}

				var day = d.getDate().toString();

				if(day.length === 1) {
					day = "0" + day;
				}

				return month + day + d.getFullYear().toString();
			}
			/**
			 * Capture booking and search events.
			 */
			var registerBookingEvent = function() {
				var millisecondsInDay = 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000;

				if($(this).prop("tagName") !== "A") {
					var activeTab = $("#booking-widget .tabs .tab.active").attr("id");

					if(activeTab == "search-tab") {
						var location = $("[name=search]").val();
					} else {
						var location = $("#booking-destination option:selected").attr("data-ctyhocn");
					}

					var current = new Date();
					var arrival = new Date($("#arrival").val());
					var departure = new Date($("#departure").val());
					var rooms = $("[name=rooms]").val();
					var adults = $("[name=adults]").val();
					var children = $("[name=children]").val();
				} else {
					var location = $(this).attr("data-ctyhocn");

					if(!location) {
						return;
					}

					var current = new Date();
					var arrival = current;
					var departure = new Date(arrival.getTime() + millisecondsInDay);
					var rooms = "1";
					var adults = "1";
					var children = "0";
				}

				var criteria = [
					rooms,							// Rooms
					adults,							// Adults
					children,						// Children
					"",								// Flex
					"",								// Points
					"",								// Special Rate Entered
					"",								// Distance
					"",								// Meeting Capacity
					"",								// Meeting Start Date
					"",								// Meeting End Date
					"",								// FnB
					""								// AV
				];

				var dateInfo = [
					formatAADate(current),														// Current Date
					formatAADate(arrival),														// Arrival Date
					formatAADate(departure),													// Departure Date
					parseInt((departure.getTime() - arrival.getTime()) / millisecondsInDay),	// Number of Days
					parseInt((arrival.getTime() - current.getTime()) / millisecondsInDay),		// Days in Advance
				];

				if(!digitalData.page.attributes) {
					digitalData.page.attributes = {};
				}

				digitalData.page.attributes.propertySearchCriteria = criteria.join(":");
				digitalData.page.attributes.propertySearchDateInfo = dateInfo.join(":");
				digitalData.page.attributes.propertySearchLocation = location;

				if(!digitalData.event) {
					digitalData.event = [];
				}

				digitalData.event[0] = {
					"eventInfo": {
						"eventAction": "bookNow"
					}
				};

				if(!digitalData.product) {
					digitalData.product = [];
				}

				digitalData.product[0] = {
					"productInfo": {
						"productID": location
					}
				};
			}

			$("#booking-destination, #arrival, #departure, [name=rooms], [name=adults], [name=children]").change(registerBookingEvent);
			$("body").on("click", "a.book-now", null, registerBookingEvent);
		});
	</script>
